notesStmt.note: Manuscript notebook of notes taken by Benjamin Rush during lectures on chemistry given by William Cullen of the University of Edinburgh. Volume 1 of 3.
Benjamin Rush began teaching at the University of Pennsylvania in 1769, and became a professor of medical theory and clinical practice in 1791. He died in 1813.
